title: 2 Bedroom/2 Bath - Master Suites with lots of storage
posting_body: ['555 S. 10th Street', '2 Bedroom / 2 Bathroom - Master Suites!', '2 full bathrooms with shower and tub.', 'Lots of storage!', 'Summer Move-In Special.', ' $2,495 for leases signed with move-ins prior to 8/9.', ' For leases signed with move-ins after 8/10, asking rent is $2,650.', ' We have limited units available.', ' Prices are subject to change based on availability.', 'Please contact: Justin Accola, property manager to schedule tours and appointments.', 'Now accepting applications!', 'Video Tour, Layouts, Photos, and additional info available at - <URL>', 'Kennedy Hall, 555 S. 10th St. Just a few minute walk to Downtown San Jose and SJSU.', 'Prime Location near Downtown San Jose', 'Apartment is approximately 900 SF', 'Large Full Kitchen w/ Full Size Appliances', '2 Master Bedrooms, each w/ Full Bathroom and Large Individual Closet Space', 'Large Living Room', 'Freshly Painted', 'Newer Lights/Fan, fixtures and more', 'Designated Parking Space', 'Coin Op Laundry On Site', 'Water and Garbage Included', 'On Site Resident Manager', 'A few blocks away from access to 280/680 and 101 freeways', 'No smoking policy', 'Security Deposit is $2,495.', 'Sorry, No Pets!', 'Please apply online at - <URL>']
